gmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過今次事件之後，我以後都唔敢接近警署，陰氣真係好重"},{"pid":"84b00d9ce65c4bdc0f8df01c8e6b9780e1b7c457","tid":1473295,"uid":118128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T20:48:47.000Z","msg":"山頂嘅朋友你哋好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19f40dbdc5ae9a88055068551e5f83655d026be","tid":1473295,"uid":245523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T20:51:51.000Z","msg":"［緊急］你地班成日係到share fb link既人同我入曬黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1473224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1473224</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b21663ab56a31a60cd3e69b0d513dc3bd69c3eee","tid":1473295,"uid":260948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T21:05:13.000Z","msg":"推post試著說<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">818， 追討黑警濫權!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818， 正視警黑合作!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXPug1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXPug1n.jpg&h=448ec9ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6079bb0560a7ed12cdba847851754431002a4d05","tid":1473295,"uid":100753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T21:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A9VpVZ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA9VpVZ5.jpg&h=badb8879&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}